<template>
  <Window :title='$_L.get("录像回放")' :width="800" style="height:550px" ref="w">
    <Toolbar ref="toolbar">
        <InputDateTime  :label="$_L.get('开始时间')"        v-model="stime" type="YMDHNS" clearable/>
        <InputDateTime  :label="$_L.get('结束时间')"        v-model="etime" type="YMDHNS" clearable/>
        <Button type="primary" :icon="'el-icon-search'" @click="onSearch()" >{{$_L.get('查询')}}</Button>
    </Toolbar>
    <PlaybackForSkip ref="PlaybackForSkip" :carId="carId" :stime="stime" :etime="etime" style="height:510px"/>
  </Window>
</template>

<script>
  export default {
    components: {
      PlaybackForSkip: () => import('@/modules/mnt/MntVideoPlaybackModule/PlaybackForSkip.vue' /*webpackChunkName:'PlaybackForSkip'*/),
    },
    data: function() {
      return {
        carId: null,
        stime: null,
        etime: null,
      };
    },
    mounted(){
    },
    methods:{
      onSearch(){
        if (this.stime > this.etime)return $_alert.warn($_L.get('开始时间不能大于结束时间！'), this.$el);
        this.$refs.PlaybackForSkip._setChns(this.carId)
      }
    }
  };
</script>
